Dear Daniyah,

I hope all is well for you! I'm writing to confirm something with you. We h=
ave you listed in our records as a member of the Class of 2025, but we know=
 that plans can change, and graduation timelines don=E2=80=99t always follo=
w a straight path.

If you=E2=80=99re graduating this year with the Class of 2026, congratulati=
ons! This is an incredible milestone, and we=E2=80=99re so proud of all tha=
t you=E2=80=99ve accomplished along the way. Your journey reflects the dedi=
cation, resilience, and commitment to scholarship, leadership, and service =
that define the NSCS community.

You may want to celebrate your NSCS nomination and membership with official=
