text"><p style=3D"line-height:175%">Dear Daniyah,</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">I hope all is well for you! I'm writing to co=
nfirm something with you. We have you listed in our records as a member of =
the <span style=3D"font-weight: bold;">Class of 2025</span>, but we know th=
at plans can change, and graduation timelines don=E2=80=99t always follow a=
 straight path.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%"><span style=3D"font-weight: bold;">If you=E2=
=80=99re graduating this year with the Class of 2026, congratulations!</spa=
n> This is an incredible milestone, and we=E2=80=99re so proud of all that =
you=E2=80=99ve accomplished along the way. Your journey reflects the dedica=
tion, resilience, and commitment to scholarship, leadership, and service th=
at define the NSCS community.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">You may want to celebrate your NSCS nominatio=
n and membership with official honor society regalia, a meaningful keepsake=
 that represents your achievements as a member of the top 20% of your class=
.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%; text-align:center" align=3D"center"><span sty=
le=3D"font-weight: bold;">You can order your NSCS graduation regalia here:<=
/span><br><a href=3D"https://email.nscs.org/e3t/Ctc/W2+113/d107Qc04/VX39JY8=
xd_SXW62Ct2x1WmK3jW2ZRfP15MgkwxN8XrLFT3lYM-W7lCdLW6lZ3lSW5Tz9RW7hF8fWW3qsxk=
c3y-J15W38rFwB2Qn8G-W6C1Ln_6FH8htW1VWdNC5zZ6tKW2_M6572xMpfwW4T_6R67rcj9GW7v=
d1gG7bjvsbN5X5cmQM8XL3W7xSldh3pvRRsW51Ryzp8j8hXrW4W7VjC8GXQJtW3BcRWX5NWC7ZW=
32YqFl2fh56tW2nxP3b1n1NMVVnb9c86hG20zW1PmB272Nxp0DW6hKpJ73jz6dXVMRlfQ4lLZYJ=
W4xG4tN3n0dplW6xvBXS4J8d7MW6DY3pY5qkJ44W2xL7WL64j6xGW8DyMWc5ZFDJwdyT-jW04" =
style=3D"color:#981b1e" data-hs-link-id=3D"1" data-hs-link-id-v2=3D"8AdEWnl=
f" target=3D"_blank">https://store.nscs.org/collections/graduation-regalia<=
/a></p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%; text-align:center" align=3D"center">Use code =
<span style=3D"color: #a99268; font-size: 15px;"><strong>FREESHIP26</strong=
></span> for <strong>free shipping through Thursday, April 16th.&nbsp;</str=
ong></p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">We=E2=80=99re proud to have you as part of th=
e NSCS community as a lifetime member!</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">With pride and appreciation,<br>Holly Barclay=
<br>Director of Chapter and Member Experience<br>The National Society of Co=
